review_title: Fun and somewhat of a workout...
one_reviews_text: I enjoyed this game... The space scenes are beautiful. Would that I had more room to move around. Not too crazy about the rail gun aspect of this, but it adds another element to keep things from being boring... I do enjoy the swinging light sabers at moving objects however... Got through a few levels and am curious to see where the rest of this game takes me...
A very nice quick game to practice if you have a couple of minutes. Nice background scene!
review_feedback: Thank you, IO, glad you liked it, and stay tuned for future updates!
